Class DroppableWebElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cognifide.qa.bb.dragdrop.DroppableWebElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Droppable

    public class DroppableWebElement
extends Object
implements Droppable
    This class wraps WebElement into Droppable interface so that the WebElement can be the target of Bobcat's drag and drop functionality.
